<main role="main">
  <section class="jumbotron text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="jumbotron-heading">Experiment.rocks</h1>
      <p class="lead text-muted">Optimize your life - one experiment at a time</p>
      <p>
        <a href="<%= categories_path %>" class="btn btn-primary my-2">View experiments</a>
        <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-secondary my-2">Register</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container marketing">

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">1. Choose an experiment</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Check out which benefits you can expect to gain and see how others rate this experiment.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        {% include icons/placeholder.svg width="500" height="500" background="#eee" color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">2. Track the impact it has on your life</h2>
        <p class="lead">Fill in a baseline survey before you start, and track your progress on a day to day basis. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
        {% include icons/placeholder.svg width="500" height="500" background="#eee" color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">3. Evaluate the results after 3 weeks</h2>
        <p class="lead">See the results in your charts and decide on whether to integrate this into your life. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        {% include icons/placeholder.svg width="500" height="500" background="#eee" color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">4. Repeat</h2>
        <p class="lead">Congratulations! You tried something new and found out whether it improved your life. When you're ready, try out a new experiment! </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
        {% include icons/placeholder.svg width="500" height="500" background="#eee" color="#aaa" class="bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">
  </div>
</main>
